        "en_title": "Katz left for Rome, will see Tajani, Crosetto and Piantedosi",
        "en_content": "Israeli Foreign Minister\nIsrael Katz left this morning for a visit\ndiplomatic. With him - he let the ministry know - families\nhostages.\n\n\nKatz will meet the deputypremier and foreign minister\nAntonio Tajani, Minister of Defense Guido Crosetto, il\nInterior Minister Matteo Piantadosi and the leaders of the\nJewish community in Italy.\n\n\n\"The meetings - he added the ministry - will focus\non the efforts to release hostages and preserve the\ninternational legitimacy for the continuation of war\nGaza.\"\n\n\n\n\n\nReproduction reserved © Copyright ANSA\n\n\n\n",
